# Local .terraform directories
**/.terraform/*
**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# Terraform state
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*

# Logs
**/*.log

# Exclude plan files
**/*.tfplan

# Sensitive override files
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# CLI configuration files
**/.terraformrc
**/terraform.rc
